urls.description: Thank you for your interest. Get quizzed on your trip! Each correct answer will earn you a spin for exciting prizes. Remarks: 1. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted, maximum of 5 participants will be chosen at random for each location to join us! 2. Closer to actual event we will send out a final registration asking you to confirm attendance.
